{"tid":209294,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"🔥 [自由] HKU EEE 有近百科主修科任你揀","createTime":"2017-04-20T06:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T11:58:05.000Z","uid":14170,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e72c97567436e9b07068a40e9921d493486df410","tid":209294,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"以下係 HKU Electrical &amp; Electronic Engineering 既主修科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以我 majoring in Electrical 為例，畢業要求有一部份要讀 8 科 4 字頭既科目，其中有 3 科一定係 from Group A，一科 Group I，然後有將近一半既自由主修科可以從下表揀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔似工業學校咁由學校揀比你讀，餵到肥肥地就推學生出去賣豬仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Aj709H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Aj709H.jpg&h=2893e59d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNr54Vg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNr54Vg.jpg&h=32e61502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2n5v3xb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2n5v3xb.jpg&h=2b7fc4bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/20/135638_8affbcb139a78e1a841332706f191dcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F20%2F135638_8affbcb139a78e1a841332706f191dcc.jpg&h=d8f8e78b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/20/135638_351143bcbddba13e18f8b9253bdf6686.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F20%2F135638_351143bcbddba13e18f8b9253bdf6686.jpg&h=fba529c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02G528a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02G528a.jpg&h=6125